text: <!channel>: good morning team! travel is all booked for our bay area visit! if you are going, you should have confirmation emails in your inbox as well as an itinerary w/ your confirmation numbers on your desk (or i handed it to you) - the plan is to fly into san jose, watch a sweet demo at the google office, drive to san bruno and see the youtube office. please take a look at your info and let me know if you see anything weird!!
and get ready because i'm driving y'all in a minivan!
